ies%20over%20up-armored%20HMMWVs%20in%20Cyprus.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c73cf069253ccddf983a7e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22641%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECyprus%20and%20the%20US%20have%20grown%20closer%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20with%20the%20former%20looking%20to%20replace%20its%20Russian%20weapons.%3Cp%3EMaj.%20Robert%20Fellingham%2F12th%20Combat%20Aviation%20Brigade%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECyprus%20has%20been%20realigning%20its%20interests%20away%20from%20Russia%20toward%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20has%20been%20replacing%20its%20Russian%20arms%2C%20and%20it%20can%20now%20acquire%20US%20weapons%20more%20easily.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20replaced%20helicopters%20and%20air%20defenses.%20A%20security%20studies%20expert%20said%20armor%20could%20be%20next.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20former%20Russian%20partner%20and%20so-called%20%26quot%3Bunsinkable%20aircraft%20carrier%26quot%3B%20strategically%20located%20in%20the%20Mediterranean%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrowing-us-cyprus-relationship-is-problem-for-russia-and-turkey-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrawn%20much%20closer%20to%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20years%20and%20can%20now%20more%20easily%20get%20its%20hands%20on%20American%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20a%20directive%20signed%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20last%20US%20administration%2C%20Cyprus%20is%20now%20included%20in%20the%20Foreign%20Military%20Sales%20(FMS)%20and%20Excess%20Defense%20Articles%20(EDA)%20programs.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20Cypriot%20National%20Guard%2C%20the%20country's%20military%20force%2C%20will%20now%20be%20able%20to%20participate%20in%20more%20training%20initiatives%20with%20US%20troops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECyprus'%20inclusion%20in%20these%20two%20programs%20is%20significant%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20as%20the%20country%20is%20continuing%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-cyprus-improve-relations-amid-russia-turkey-mediterranean-tensions-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWestern%20reorientation%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20slowly%20phasing%20out%20its%20Russian%20arms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228813517a-7df2-4b40-825a-0684dba48483%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECome%20and%20buy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Foreign%20Military%20Sales%20program%20enables%20the%20Department%20of%20Defense%20to%20purchase%20weapons%20directly%20from%20US%20arms%20manufacturers%20on%20behalf%20of%20partner%20countries%2C%20simplifying%20the%20process%20for%20the%20buyer.%20And%20the%20Excess%20Defense%20Articles%20program%20allows%20partner%20countries%20to%20acquire%20excess%20US%20defense%20equipment%20for%20free%20or%20at%20significantly%20discounted%20prices%20to%20modernize%20their%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%201987%20US%20arms%20embargo%20previously%20led%20the%20Cypriot%20government%20to%20turn%20to%20Russia%20for%20many%20of%20its%20weapons%20while%20pursuing%20a%20close%20relationship%20with%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20Russians%20invaded%20Ukraine%20in%202022%2C%20Cyprus%20has%20been%20distancing%20itself%20from%20Moscow%20and%20has%20been%20steadily%20replacing%20its%20Russian%20weapons.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20partially%20lifted%20the%20arms%20embargo%20in%202020%20and%20two%20years%20later%20fully%20lifted%20it%20subject%20to%20a%20yearly%20evaluation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Cyprus%20replaced%20its%20Russian%20Mil%20Mi-35P%20attack%20helicopters%20with%20French%20Airbus%20ones%2C%20and%20last%20December%2C%20it%20bought%20Israeli%20Barak%208%20surface-to-air%20missile%20systems%20to%20replace%20its%20Russian%20TOR%20M-1%20and%20Buk%20SAMs.%20Beyond%20vehicles%20and%20air%20defenses%2C%20vehicles%20could%20be%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20policy%20of%20divesting%20itself%20from%20Russian%20equipment%20is%20proceeding%2C%20two%20major%20purchases%20represent%20next%20logical%20projects%3A%20main%20battle%20tanks%20and%20armored%20fighting%20vehicles%2C%26quot%3B%20Andrew%20Novo%2C%20a%20strategic%20studies%20professor%20at%20the%20National%20Defense%20University%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222801%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Ukrainian%20serviceman%20of%20the%2047th%20Magura%20Separate%20Mechanized%20Brigade%20is%20seen%20near%20a%20M2%20Bradley%20infantry%20fighting%20vehicle%20for%20combat%20activities%20at%20a%20position%20near%20a%20front%20line%2C%20amid%20Russia's%20attack%20on%20Ukraine%2C%20in%20Zaporizhzhia%20region%2C%20Ukraine%20September%206%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64fb1f603d3923001976a57d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222040%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20M2%20Bradley%2C%20an%20armored%20fighting%20vehicle%2C%20has%20proved%20itself%20in%20Ukraine.%3Cp%3EREUTERS%2FStringer%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Cypriot%20National%20Guard%20uses%20Russian%20T-80%20main%20battle%20tanks%20and%20BMP-3%20armored%20fighting%20vehicles%2C%20so%20%26quot%3BAmerican%20M1%20tanks%20and%20Bradley%20M2%20(or%20other)%20armored%20vehicles%20would%20be%20logical%20candidates%20to%20replace%20existing%20stocks%2C%26quot%3B%20Novo%20said.%20Patrol%20boats%20up%20to%20Corvette-size%20units%2C%20assault%20rifles%2C%20and%20communications%20equipment%20could%20also%20be%20a%20priority%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20M1%20Abrams%20tanks%20and%20Bradley%20armored%20fighting%20vehicles%20are%20highly%20regarded%2C%20and%20the%20Bradleys%20have%20famously%20proven%20their%20worth%20in%20the%20battlefields%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20even%20squaring%20off%20against%20tanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20Cyprus's%20current%20weapons%20could%20end%20up%20there%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20had%C2%A0initially%C2%A0rejected%20the%20idea%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrowing-us-cyprus-relationship-is-problem-for-russia-and-turkey-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esending%20its%20old%20Russian%20weapons%20to%20Ukraine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20citing%20concerns%20for%20its%20own%20security%20%E2%80%94%20since%20a%20Turkish%20invasion%20in%201974%2C%20the%20island's%20northern%20third%20has%20been%20occupied%20by%20Turkish%20forces%20and%20de-facto%20seceded%20%E2%80%94%20acquiring%20US%20systems%20could%20allow%20it%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20a%20possibility%20could%20be%20considered%20provided%20that%20this%20equipment%20is%20replaced%20with%20equivalent%20or%20better%20equipment%2C%26quot%3B%20then-Cypriot%20president%20Nicos%20Anastasiades%20had%20said%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229c8a1ff3-af8e-42e5-b862-a127dfdc5620%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELooking%20ahead%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20what%20direction%20the%20new%20Trump%20administration%20may%20take%20things%2C%20but%20Cyprus's%20inclusion%20in%20these%20programs%20could%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20a%20full%20lifting%20of%20the%20weapons%20embargo%2C%20removing%20the%20yearly%20evaluation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20solidify%20relations%20with%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChanging%20the%20evaluations%20could%20mean%20big%20changes.%20%26quot%3BIn%20general%2C%20adopting%20a%20new%20weapons%20system%20is%20a%20multiyear%20process%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%26quot%3B%20Novo%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Cypriot%20government%20cannot%20order%20an%20American%20weapons%20system%20and%20risk%20maintenance%20or%20procurement%20based%20on%20a%20year-by-year%20waiver.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20countries%20are%20strengthening%20their%20military%20collaboration%20in%20other%20ways%2C%20too.%20In%20September%2C%20they%20signed%20a%20defense%20cooperation%20framework%20agreement%20to%20better%20respond%20to%20humanitarian%20crises%20and%20security%20concerns%20and%20enhance%20interoperability%20between%20US%20and%20Cypriot%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECypriot%20special%20operations%20units%20have%20been%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-us-partner-cyprus-increased-western-special-operations-activity-mediterranean-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20frequently%20training%20with%20their%20US%20counterparts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20in%202023%2C%20a%20US%20nuclear-powered%20submarine%20docked%20in%20the%20Cypriot%20port%20of%20Limassol%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226368%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22East%20Coast-based%20U.S.%20Naval%20Special%20Warfare%20Operators%20(SEALs)%20and%20Special%20Warfare%20Combatant-Craft%20Crewmen%20(SWCC)%20conduct%20maritime%20training%20with%20Cypriot%20Underwater%20Demolition%20Command%20(MYK)%20forces%20near%20Limassol%2C%20Cyprus%20on%20Jan.%2025%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65f2fba5857f90b715226ddc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224245%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20has%20been%20increased%20military%20cooperation%20between%20the%20US%20and%20Cyprus%2C%20including%20in%20the%20special%20operations%20space.%3Cp%3EUS%20Navy%20photo%20by%20Mass%20Communication%20Specialist%201st%20Class%20Bill%20Carlisle%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20Marines%20and%20aircraft%20deployed%20to%20Cyprus%20last%20year%20in%20preparation%20for%20a%20potential%20evacuation%20of%20US%20citizens%20from%20Lebanon%2C%20and%20now%2C%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%20is%20considering%20upgrading%20Cyprus's%20main%20air%20base%20to%20use%20it%20for%20humanitarian%20operations%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20island%20sits%20at%20a%20strategic%20location%20in%20the%20eastern%20Mediterranean%2C%20only%20about%20100%20miles%20from%20the%20Levant%2C%20and%20provides%20access%20to%20North%20Africa%20and%20Asia%20Minor.%20It%20has%20often%20been%20described%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bunsinkable%20aircraft%20carrier.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Cypriot%20president%20has%20expressed%20his%20commitment%20to%20expand%20his%20country's%20defense%20and%20security%20cooperation%20with%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20to%20the%20best%20interest%20of%20both%20the%20US%20and%20Cyprus%20to%20maintain%20and%20develop%20this%20relationship%2C%20and%20the%20US%20is%20proving%20that%20by%20investing%20in%20defense%20and%20security%20infrastructure%20in%20Cyprus%2C%26quot%3B%20Novo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrategic-island-cyprus-more-easily-swap-russian-weapons-for-american-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741220162000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c7971ab1834fe311662a05%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrategic-island-cyprus-more-easily-swap-russian-weapons-for-american-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20and%20Cyprus%20are%20forging%20closer%20ties.%20New%20agreements%20let%20the%20strategic%20Mediterranean%20island%20nation%20more%20easily%20buy%20US%20weapons.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Constantine%20Atlamazoglou)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrategic-island-cyprus-more-easily-swap-russian-weapons-for-american-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Khalistani%20extremists%20heckle%2C%20attempt%20to%20attack%20S%20Jaishankar%20in%20London%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741220075000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118746413%2Cimgsize-894988.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fkhalistani-extremists-heckle-attempt-to-attack-eam-jaishankar-in-london-man-tears-indian-flag%2Farticlesh