sed%2C%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20reservations%2C%20and%20we%20will%20accommodate%20them.%20But%20don't%20link%20all%20issues%20at%20a%20time.%26quot%3B%20Speaking%20about%20India's%20demographic%20potential%2C%20Naidu%20highlighted%20the%20country's%20unique%20position%20in%20the%20global%20demographic%20landscape%2C%20describing%20India%20as%20having%20the%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20advantage%20of%20demographic%20dividend%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaidu%20also%20drew%20attention%20to%20the%20global%20aging%20crisis%2C%20pointing%20out%20the%20population%20challenges%20in%20countries%20like%20Japan%2C%20China%2C%20and%20some%20European%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJapan%20is%20minus%208%20per%20cent.%20It%20is%20an%20important%20issue%20for%20the%20survival%20of%20human%20beings%2C%26quot%3B%20Naidu%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAging%20problem%20has%20started%20in%20south%20India.%20Only%20two%20states%20--%20Bihar%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20--%20have%20advantages%20in%20north%20India.%20We%20were%20thinking%20it%20is%20a%20disadvantage%20but%20it%20is%20an%20advantage%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChallenging%20the%20traditional%20family%20planning%20perspectives%2C%20Naidu%20revealed%20a%20personal%20policy%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20I%20used%20to%20advocate%20family%20planning%20as%20a%20challenge.%20Now%2C%20I%20am%20changing%20my%20views%20and%20promoting%20population%20growth%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20also%20suggested%20a%20new%20approach%20for%20resource%20allocation%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWealth%20creation%20and%20population%20often%20conflict.%26quot%3B%20He%20proposed%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20government%20of%20India%20or%20the%20finance%20commission%20should%20promote%20population%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20punish%20those%20who%20have%20aging%20problems%20today.%20Give%20incentives%20for%20more%20children%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20s