22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F118741024.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%E2%80%8BThe%20meetings%20were%20held%20in%20secrecy%20between%20US%20presidential%20envoy%20for%20hostage%20affairs%20Adam%20Boehler%20and%20Hamas%20officials.%20Israel%20was%20not%20informed%20of%20what%20was%20discussed%20at%20these%20direct%20meetings%20as%20the%20Axios%20report%20said%20that%20Israel%20learnt%20%26quot%3Babout%20aspects%20of%20the%20talks%20through%20other%20channels%26quot%3B.%20However%2C%20the%20Trump%20administration%20consulted%20with%20Israel%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20engaging%20with%20Hamas%2C%20the%20report%20added.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fus-held-direct-talks-with-hamas-in-secret-unprecedented-meetings-in-doha-report%2Farticleshow%2F118741024.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fus-held-direct-talks-with-hamas-in-secret-unprecedented-meetings-in-doha-report%2Famp_articleshow%2F118741024.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fus-held-direct-talks-with-hamas-in-secret-unprecedented-meetings-in-doha-report%2Famp_articleshow%2F118741024.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Holds%20Unprecedented%20Secret%20Talks%20With%20Hamas%20On%20Gaza%20Hostages%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Trump%20administration%20has%20been%20conducting%20secret%20talks%20with%20Hamas%20on%20the%20possibility%20of%20releasing%20U.S.%20hostages%20being%20held%20in%20Gaza%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2025%2F03%2F05%2Fus-hamas-talks-gaza-war-israel%5C%22%3EAxios%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20citing%20two%20unnamed%20sources%20with%20direct%20knowledge%20of%20the%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20important%20part%20about%20this%20talk%20is%20that%20US%20has%20never%20engaged%20with%20Hamas%20directly%20before%2C%20as%20it%20has%20designated%20it%20as%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20in%201997.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20talk%20has%20been%20held%20by%C2%A0U.S.%20presidential%20envoy%20for%20hostage%20affairs%20Adam%20Boehler%20with%20Hamas%20in%20Doha%20in%20the%20past%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20US%20government%20had%20spoken%20to%20Israel%20about%20the%20possibility%20of%20holding%20talks%20with%20Hamas%2C%20Israel%20learned%20about%20the%20engagement%20through%20other%20channels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20talks%20with%20Hamas%20have%20been%20regarding%20American%20hostages%2C%20but%20according%20to%20the%20sources%2C%20talks%20of%20a%20broader%20deal%20to%20release%20all%20remaining%20hostages%20have%20also%20been%20had%2C%20in%20order%20to%20reach%20a%20long-term%20truce.%20However%2C%20no%20deal%20has%20been%20reached%20as%20of%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESteve%20Witkoff%2C%20special%20envoy%20to%20the%20White%20House%20planned%20to%20meet%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20Qatar%20regarding%20ceasefire%20negotiations%2C%20but%20cancelled%20the%20trip%20after%20he%20saw%20that%20there%20was%20no%20interest%20from%20Hamas%2C%20per%20a%20US%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20repeatedly%20threatened%20Hamas%20with%20%26quot%3Bhell%20to%20pay%26quot%3B%20and%20has%20even%20proposed%20a%20US%20takeover%20of%20Gaza.%20Secretive%20negotiations%20with%20Hamas%20is%20something%20other%20administrations%20have%20not%20explored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%2059%20hostages%20are%20held%20by%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%20with%20the%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20confirming%2035%20dead.%20Among%20the%20remaining%20hostages%2C%20there%20are%205%20American%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20Gaza%20hostage%20deal%20expired%20on%20Saturday%20and%20no