around%20the%20complex%20case%20of%20triple%20murders%20and%20alleged%20attempted%20suicides%20that%20sent%20shockwaves%20across%20the%20city%20last%20month.%20On%20February%2019%2C%20three%20members%20of%20a%20family%20were%20found%20dead%20in%20their%20home%20in%20Tangra%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Kolkata.%20The%20case%20came%20to%20light%20when%20two%20brothers%20and%20the%20son%20of%20one%20of%20them%20crashed%20their%20car%20into%20a%20pillar%2C%20allegedly%20to%20die%20by%20suicide.%20When%20they%20were%20questioned%20by%20the%20police%2C%20they%20disclosed%20about%20the%20bodies%20in%20their%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20one%20of%20the%20brothers%2C%20Prasun%20Dey%2C%20has%20confessed%20that%20he%20killed%20all%20three%20-%20wife%20Romi%20Dey%2C%20their%2014-year-old%20daughter%20and%20sister-in-law%20Sudeshna%20Dey.%20It%20was%20revealed%20during%20his%20questioning%20that%20a%20Rs%2016%20crore%20debt%20could%20have%20led%20to%20the%20murders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brothers%20-%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkolkata-news%2Fkolkata-triple-murder-tangra-murders-no-outsider-involved-2-brothers-behind-murders-say-cops-7797154%5C%22%3EPranay%20and%20Prasun%20Dey%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20lived%20with%20their%20wives%20in%20the%20Tangra%20home.%20Pranay%20Dey's%20son%20and%20Prasun%20Dey's%20daughter%20were%20the%20other%20occupants%20of%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20chilling%20testimony%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Mr%20Dey%20-%20a%20businessman%20-%20revealed%20that%20he%20had%20first%20made%20a%20pact%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20brother%20and%20brother's%20wife%20to%20die%20by%20suicide%20over%20the%20staggering%20debt.%20The%20murders%20were%20a%20fallout%20of%20the%20failed%20suicide%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Suicide%20Pact%20That%20Led%20To%20Murders%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2017%2C%20the%20family%20of%20six%20had%20'%3Cem%3Epayesh%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(rice%20pudding)%20mixed%20with%20sle