20Not%20Getting...%26quot%3B%3A%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20pace%20spearhead%20Mohammed%20Shami%20has%20broken%20ranks%20by%20admitting%20that%20playing%20all%20their%20Champions%20Trophy%20games%20at%20one%20venue%20in%20Dubai%20has%20been%20to%20their%20advantage.%20Shami%20returned%20figures%20of%203-48%20to%20set%20up%20India's%20four-wicket%20win%20over%20Australia%20in%20the%20semi-finals%20on%20Tuesday%20in%20Dubai.%20India%20coach%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gautam%20Gambhir%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F563-gautam-gambhir-playerprofile%5C%22%3EGautam%20Gambhir%3C%2Fa%3E%20afterwards%20lashed%20out%20at%20critics%20who%20have%20said%20playing%20at%20the%20same%20Dubai%20International%20Cricket%20Stadium%20each%20time%20is%20unfair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20refused%20to%20travel%20to%20Champions%20Trophy%20hosts%20Pakistan%20over%20political%20tensions%20and%20have%20won%20all%20four%20of%20their%20games%20at%20their%20temporary%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20will%20face%20South%20Africa%20or%20New%20Zealand%20in%20Sunday's%20final%2C%20again%20in%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20seven%20teams%20in%20the%20ODI%20competition%20have%20meanwhile%20had%20to%20shuttle%20between%20three%20Pakistani%20cities%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20definitely%20helped%20us%20because%20we%20know%20the%20conditions%20and%20the%20behaviour%20of%20the%20pitch%2C%26quot%3B%20Shami%20said%20Tuesday%20after%20his%20pivotal%20role%20in%20beating%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20plus%20point%20that%20you%20are%20playing%20all%20the%20matches%20at%20one%20venue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20hybrid%20arrangement%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%20South%20Africa%20were%20forced%20to%20travel%20to%20Dubai%2C%20only%20to%20return%20to%20Pakistan%20again%20less%20than%2024%20hours%20later%20without%20playing%20a%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20are%20unbeaten%20in%20the%2010%20ODIs%20they%20have%20played%20in%20Dubai%2C%20winning%20nine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'World%20class'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShami%2C%2034%2C%20claimed%20a%20five-wicket%20haul%20in%20India's%20opening%20win%20over%20Bangladesh%20and%20has%20bowled%20with%20pace%20and%20accuracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20question%20on%20getting%20reverse%20swing%20with%20the%20old%20ball%20got%20Shami%20pleading%20with%20cricket%20authorities%20to%20allow%20the%20use%20of%20saliva%20to%20polish%20the%20ball%20in%20the%2050-over%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20in%202022%20made%20a%20ban%20on%20saliva%20--%20brought%20in%20during%20the%20Covid%20pandemic%20--%20permanent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20trying%20to%20reverse%2C%20but%20you%20are%20not%20getting%20the%20use%20of%20saliva%20into%20the%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20Shami%20told%20reporters.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20constantly%20appealing%20to%20allow%20the%20use%20of%20saliva%20and%20it%20will%20be%20interesting%20with%20the%20reverse%20swing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20saliva%20to%20shine%20one%20side%20of%20the%20old%20ball%20and%20keep%20the%20other%20rough%20helps%20fast%20bowlers%20get%20the%20leather%20ball%20to%20swing%20late%20and%20can%20be%20a%20lethal%20weapon%20in%20the%20final%20few%20overs%20of%20an%20ODI%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20can%20still%20use%20sweat.%20After%20a%20strong%20start%20to%20the%20tournament%2C%20Shami%20left%20the%20field%20briefly%20in%20the%20win%20over%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20now%20put%20all%20fears%20of%20any%20fitness%20issues%20to%20rest%20with%20two%20matches%20in%20three%20days%20and%20bowling%20his%20full%20quota%20of%2010%20overs%20against%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20trying%20to%20get%20my%20rhythm%20back%20and%20contribute%20more%20for%20the%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Shami.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20ready%20to%20bowl%20long%20spells.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGambhir%20called%20Shami%20%26quot%3Ba%20world-class%20performer%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20phenomenal%20and%20the%20hunger%20he%20brings%20on%20the%20table%2C%20the%20way%20he%20trains%2C%20the%20way%20he%20practises%20--%20that's%20why%20you%20see%20all%20those%20results.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741192020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fm3tv5938_mohammed-shami_625x300_05_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fconstantly-appealing-mohammed-shamis-desperate-plea-to-icc-on-repealing-covid-times-law-7856226%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mohammed%20Shami%2C%2034%2C%20claimed%20a%20five-wicket%20haul%20in%20India's%20opening%20win%20over%20Bangladesh%20and%20has%20bowled%20with%20pace%20and%20accuracy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fconstantly-appealing-mohammed-shamis-desperate-plea-to-icc-on-repealing-covid-times-law-7856226%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Semiconductor%20Mission%2C%20Tata%20ink%20fiscal%20pact%20for%20Gujarat%20chip%20plant%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741191987000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Findia-semiconductor-mission-tata-ink-fiscal-pact-for-gujarat-chip-plant-125030501282_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Centre%20through%20the%20India%20Semiconductor%20Mission%2C%20has%20committed%2050%20per%20cent%20fiscal%20support%20on%20a%20pari-passu%20basis%20for%20eligible%20project%20costs%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Findia-semiconductor-mission-tata-ink-fiscal-pact-for-gujarat