tedly%20said%20the%20battle%20between%20the%20Mughal%20emperor%20and%20Chhatrapati%20Sambhaji%20Maharaj%20was%20for%20state%20administration%20and%20not%20about%20Hindu%20and%20Muslim.%20Later%2C%20he%20said%20his%20words%20had%20been%20twisted%20and%20he%20would%20take%20them%20back%20and%20apologise%20if%20sentiments%20were%20hurt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20words%20have%20been%20twisted.%20I%20have%20said%20what%20historians%20and%20writers%20have%20said%20about%20Aurangzeb%20Rahmatullah%20Ali%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Azmi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20zero%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20was%20filed%20against%20Mr%20Azmi%20with%20Naupada%20police%20station%20in%20Thane.%20It%20was%20then%20transferred%20to%20Marine%20Drive%20police%20station%20in%20Mumbai.%20A%20zero%20FIR%20is%20filed%20in%20any%20location%2C%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20relevant%20police%20station%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20was%20filed%20based%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20Shiv%20Sena%20MP%20Naresh%20Mhaske.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYogi%20Adityanath%20said%20the%20recently%20concluded%20Maha%20Kumbh%20will%20remain%20a%20memorable%20event%20for%20people%20across%20India%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaha%20Kumbh%20in%20Prayagraj%20was%20a%20memorable%20event%20for%20everyone%20who%20came%20from%20all%20over%20the%20country%20and%20the%20world.%20It%20was%20a%20unique%20event%20which%20will%20continue%20to%20attract%20people.%20People%20have%20their%20own%20issues%2C%20emotions.%20Neither%20we%20impose%20it%20on%20anyone%20nor%20we%20have%20this%20kind%20of%20nature.%20During%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20political%20parties%20badmouthed%20it%2C%20but%20we%20remained%20silent%20and%20performed%20our%20duties%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20UP%20chief%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741188720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fj44kcpkg_yogi-adityanath_625x300_05_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22htt