ecially%20as%20Baran%20is%20home%20to%20Rajasthan%20Education%20Minister%20Madan%20Dilawar.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20had%20visited%20the%20school%20recently%20to%20look%20into%20the%20issue.%20Sources%20said%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20people%20found%20guilty%20in%20this%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20invitation%20card%20for%20the%20school's%20farewell%20party%20for%20outgoing%20students%20of%20Class%2012%20had%20the%20Urdu%20words%20%26quot%3BJashan%20e%20Alvida%26quot%3B%20written%20under%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20Goddess%20Saraswati.%20A%20section%20of%20parents%20and%20students%20had%20taken%20offence%20and%20the%20matter%20was%20reported%20to%20the%20Education%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESchool%20principal%20Vikesh%20Kumar%20said%20there%20were%20some%20Muslim%20students%20in%20the%20school%20and%20they%20had%20suggested%20this%20title%20for%20the%20function.%20Then%2C%20at%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20School%20Development%20Management%20Committee%2C%20the%20parents%20had%20given%20their%20approval.%20Only%20after%20this%2C%20the%20invitation%20cards%20were%20printed%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20after%20printing%20the%20cards%2C%20we%20realised%20that%20this%20name%20was%20not%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20government%20language.%20Then%20we%20took%20back%20most%20of%20the%20cards.%20But%20some%20cards%20remained%20with%20the%20students%2C%20whose%20pictures%20later%20went%20viral%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajasthan%20government's%20move%20to%20replace%20Urdu%20with%20Sanskrit%20has%20made%20headlines%20recently.%20The%20government%20had%20contended%20that%20this%20is%20because%20it%20has%20been%20found%20many%20teaching%20the%20language%20have%20fake%20degrees%20-%20an%20allegation%20vehemently%20refuted%20by%20the%20Urdu%20Teachers'%20Association.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20came%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20government%20ordering%20the%20%26quot%3