2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fexternal-affairs-defence-security%2Fnews%2Fus-eyes-zero-tariff-on-cars-in-india-trade-deal-as-tesla-entry-nears-125030501140_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elon%20Musk%20has%20now%20found%20support%20from%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20has%20repeatedly%20railed%20against%20India's%20high%20taxes%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fexternal-affairs-defence-security%2Fnews%2Fus-eyes-zero-tariff-on-cars-in-india-trade-deal-as-tesla-entry-nears-125030501140_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20The%20US%20Is%20Killing%20Someone%20By%20Firing%20Squad%20For%20The%20First%20Time%20In%2015%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20firing%20squad%2C%20a%20method%20of%20execution%20with%20a%20long%20and%20complex%20history%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20is%20set%20to%20be%20used%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%2015%20years%20in%20South%20Carolina.%20On%20Friday%2C%20Brad%20Sigmon%2C%20convicted%20of%20murdering%20his%20ex-girlfriend's%20parents%20in%202001%2C%20will%20face%20a%20firing%20squad%2C%20a%20method%20he%20chose%20over%20the%20electric%20chair%20and%20lethal%20injection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20history%20of%20firing%20squads%20in%20the%20US%20dates%20back%20to%20colonial%20times%2C%20when%20it%20was%20used%20as%20a%20punishment%20for%20mutiny.%20In%201608%2C%20captain%20George%20Kendall%2C%20was%20executed%20by%20firing%20squad%20in%20Jamestown%2C%20Virginia%2C%20for%20suspected%20mutiny%20and%20conspiracy%20with%20Spain.%20This%20marked%20the%20first%20recorded%20execution%20by%20shooting%20in%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Civil%20War%2C%20firing%20squads%20were%20used%20by%20both%20sides%20to%20execute%20deserters%20and%20create%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20spectacle%E2%80%9D%20to%20maintain%20discipline.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Ffiring-squad-death-penalty-south-carolina-sigmon-05000e874b12bb67c00832c2230f42c8%5C%22%3EAssociated%20Press%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mark%20Smith%2C%20a%20history%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20South%20Carolina%2C%20firing%20squads%20were%20designed%20to%20shock%20and%20intimidate%2C%20with%20the%20added%20element%20of%20uncertainty%2C%20as%20one%20of%20the%20executioners%20would%20often%20be%20given%20a%20blank%20cartridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20late%2019th%20and%20early%2020th%20centuries%2C%20Utah%20became%20the%20primary%20state%20to%20use%20firing%20squads%2C%20with%20at%20least%2040%20executions%20carried%20out%20by%20this%20method.%20One%20notable%20case%20was%20the%20execution%20of%20labour%20activist%20and%20songwriter%20Joe%20Hill%20in%201915.%20Hill%2C%20who%20maintained%20his%20innocence%20until%20the%20end%2C%20was%20shot%20by%20a%20firing%20squad%20in%20Utah%20State%20Prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20use%20of%20firing%20squads%20declined%20as%20lethal%20injection%20became%20the%20preferred%20method%20of%20execution%20in%20the%201980s.%20Lethal%20injection%20was%20initially%20seen%20as%20a%20more%20humane%20alternative%2C%20but%20it%20has%20since%20been%20plagued%20by%20botched%20executions%20and%20difficulties%20in%20obtaining%20the%20required%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20however%2C%20some%20states%20have%20reconsidered%20firing%20squads%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20lethal%20injection.%20According%20to%20Deborah%20Denno%2C%20a%20criminologist%20at%20Fordham%20School%20of%20Law%2C%20firing%20squads%20have%20been%20relatively%20reliable%2C%20with%20only%20two%20reported%20cases%20of%20botched%20executions.%20Denno%20has%20argued%20that%20firing%20squads%20may%20be%20a%20more%20humane%20alternative%20to%20lethal%20injection%2C%20as%20they%20are%20typically%20quicker%20and%20less%20prone%20to%20error.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20South%20Carolina%2C%20Sigmon's%20decision%20to%20choose%20the%20firing%20squad%20over%20other%20methods%20has%20sparked%20debate.%20His%20attorney%2C%20Gerald%20%E2%80%9CBo%E2%80%9D%20King%2C%20stated%20that%20Sigmon%20chose%20the%20firing%20squad%20because%20the%20alternatives%20seemed%20worse.%20The%20execution%20will%20be%20carried%20out%20by%20volunteer%20officers%2C%20with%20Sigmon%20bound%20to%20a%20chair%20and%20a%20target%20placed%20over%20his%20heart.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20US%20continues%20to%20grapple%20with%20the%20ethics%20and%20practicalities%20of%20capital%20punishment%2C%20the%20use%20of%20firing%20squads%20raises%20complex%20questions%20about%20the%20nature%20of%20justice%20and%20the%20value%20of%20human%20life.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741185360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fsgf5m6gg_execution-istock_625x300_05_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-the-us-is-killing-someone-by-firing-squad-for-the-first-time-in-15-years-7855707%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20Friday%2C%20Brad%20Sigmon%2C%20convicted%20of%20murdering%20his%20ex-girlfriends%20parents%20in%202001%2C%20will%20face%20a%20firing%20squad%2C%20a%20method%20he%20chose%20over%20the%20electric%20chair%20and%20lethal%20injection.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-the-us-is-killing-someone-by-firing-squad-for-the-first-time-in-15-years-7855707%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chandan%20Roy%20Sanyal%20on%20%E2%80%98Aashram%E2%80%99%20backlash%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741185182000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118738588%2Cimgsize-47872.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fhindi%2Fchandan-roy-sanyal-on-aashram-backlash-if-the-show-had-only-received-critic