ares%20Ruchika.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20created%20themed%20items%2C%20like%20safari-themed%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F404094%2Fcode-effort-recycling-cigarette-butts-into-sustainable-products-plush-toys-creating-jobs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplush%20toys%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20elephants%20and%20giraffes%2C%20to%20make%20it%20more%20fun%20and%20personal.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20duo%20also%20designed%20matching%20clothes%20with%20a%20twist%20as%20part%20of%20their%20gifting%20collection.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20believe%20that%20while%20twins%20may%20look%20alike%2C%20they%20each%20have%20their%20personalities%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20continues.%20%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20created%20designs%20like%20apples%20and%20oranges%20prints%2C%20symbolising%20how%20twins%20may%20be%20similar%20in%20appearance%20but%20unique%20in%20their%20personalities.%20And%20of%20course%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20kept%20the%20cute%20packaging%20in%20mind.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOffering%20more%20than%20just%20products%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEvery%20product%20has%20a%20reason%20behind%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nikita%20adds.%20The%20startup%20started%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20building%20a%20supportive%20community%20where%20twin%20parents%20could%20share%20experiences%2C%20advice%2C%20and%20solutions%20to%20the%20challenges%20they%20faced.%20%E2%80%9CI%20felt%20left%20out%20during%20my%20early%20days%20of%20motherhood%20because%20single%20parents%20were%20unable%20to%20relate%20to%20my%20problems%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ruchika%20confesses.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20feeling%20of%20isolation%20is%20common%20for%20many%20twin%20parents.%20We%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20space%20where%20they%20could%20connect%20and%20know%20they%20are%20not%20alone.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TwinsTribe%20WhatsApp%20group%20has%20grown%20rapidly%2C%20with%20over%20750%20members%2C%20and%20it%E2%