ouring%20unless%20prompted%20by%20officials.%20It%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20with%20such%20a%20state%20of%20mind%2C%20he%20is%20ruling%20Bihar.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20maintained%20that%20Mr%20Kumar%20had%20%26quot%3Bbrought%20disrepute%20to%20Bihar%20by%20touching%20the%20feet%20of%20Modi%20last%20year%2C%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20many%20other%20chief%20ministers%2C%20when%20the%20new%20Union%20government%20was%20being%20sworn%20in.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20he%20has%20so%20much%20of%20reverence%20for%20the%20PM%2C%20he%20could%20have%20touched%20the%20latter's%20feet%20in%20private.%20But%20he%20is%20resorting%20to%20sycophancy%20merely%20to%20keep%20himself%20in%20the%20chair.%20Why%20does%20he%20not%20use%20his%20clout%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20is%20now%20dependent%20on%20JD(U)'s%20support%20to%20survive%20in%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20to%20revive%20the%20moribund%20sugar%20industry%20in%20Bihar%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kishor%20asked.%3Cbr%3E%5CnHe%20said%20the%20Jan%20Suraaj%20Party%20will%20enter%20the%20fray%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20pull%20Bihar%20%26quot%3Bout%20of%20the%20political%20rut%20which%20has%20been%20held%20hostage%20for%20decades%20by%20Kumar%20and%20his%20arch-rival%20Lalu%20Prasad%2C%20the%20RJD%20president%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20had%20helped%20the%20RJD%20survive%20in%20powers%20for%20many%20years%2C%20share%20the%20blame%20for%20Bihar's%20plight%2C%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECriticising%20the%20state's%20much-touted%20prohibition%20policy%2C%20Mr%20Kishor%20said%20that%20the%20ban%20on%20liquor%20in%20Bihar%20is%20yet%20another%20example%20of%20the%20BJP's%20duplicity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20does%20it%20(BJP)%20not%20ask%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20in%20adjoining%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20chief%20ministers%20of%20other%20states%20ruled%20by%20it%20to%20declare%20the%20same%3F%20In%20other%20states%2C%20they%20are%20talking%